  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Goal! is a soccer game from an angled overhead point of view, with the screen scrolling to follow the action.\n\nYou play with a full team of 11 players, each one rated in 7 different skill categories. You can match them against a team controlled by the computer or another player. You can even team up with a friend and match your combined skills against the best computer team.\n\nSeveral game modes are available, including tournament mode, world cup mode, and a goal shooting competition.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
